`make extract` to create translation template (source) file sl1fw.pot
`make clean` to remove all generated files
`make compile` or `make` to compile all files in $LANG/LC_MESSAGES/sl1fw.po

remote_install.sh should copy all generated files to the printer

How to set language on printer (persistent, only once):
- log in via ssh
- `localectl set-locale $LOCALE.utf8`
- `systemctl restart sl1fw`
- `systemctl restart sla-client`

$LOCALE is one from en_US, cs_CZ, de_DE, es_ES, fr_FR, it_IT, pl_PL
